00:02:21.810 --> 00:02:23.500
going to be similar triangles.

00:02:23.500 --> 00:02:25.860
You have an angle
right over here.

00:02:25.860 --> 00:02:29.390
And the ratio of 6/2 is
the same thing as 3/1.

00:02:29.390 --> 00:02:32.890
The ratio of 9/3 is the
